<h1 class="card-title">Dream Avenue Font</h1>
<div class="entry-content">
<p>Dream Avenue fonts include uppercase letters, lowercase letters, numerals, a large range of punctuation. Serif font with modern classic style. Created for poster, web design, branding, illustrations, badges, and some other works.</p>
<p> Dream Avenue Font Download is available free from 8font.com.  Dream Avenue Font is a <a href="https://8font.com/category/basic-font/" rel="category tag">Basic</a>,<a href="https://8font.com/category/serif-fonts/" rel="category tag">Serif</a>  type font that can be used on any device such as PC, Mac, Linux, iOS and Android. 
this font created by Muntab_Art</p>
